    <ul class="home-block__list">
      <li>Consistent flavor you can rely on</li>
      <li>Simple, fast checkout experience</li>
      <li>Clean product design — no confusion</li>
      <li>Built to become part of your daily routine</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section-shell home-block">
    <h2 class="home-block__title">This Is Just the Beginning</h2>
    <p class="home-block__copy">
      Avrrio is being built as a clean, focused brand.
      One product today. A full ecosystem tomorrow.
    </p>
    <p class="home-block__copy">We start with coffee — and expand with intention.</p>
  </section>
</main>
